<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7354> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7354" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 129. His relatively early place in the consilium listed in the SC de agro Pergameno (no. 16) and the date invalidate attempts to identify him with C. Licinius Nerva (124). Tr. pl. between 120 and 111. L. R. Taylor (VDRR 224-225) suggests C. Licinius Crassus (52). Tr. pl. 145. See Sherk, RDGE no. 12, pp. 63-73. But see above, on M'. Aquillius (10), on the date.\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7354 .
